{"tid":1897371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"*資訊科技界*未登記做選民（功能組別）既同我入黎","createTime":"2020-02-25T16:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T07:15:33.000Z","uid":41355,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"c33fadcee92ffcb943c622e58bf2697cbdb3b975","tid":1897371,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:35:45.000Z","msg":"想係9月立法會入面投到功能界別票，只要完成以下三部曲<br />\n1) 登記成為地方選區選民 (相信大家一早登記左)<br />\n2) <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">加入符合 IT 界選民資格的組織</span></strong><br />\n3) 填寫及遞交功能界別選民登記表格 REO-41<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=06f528f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C</a>).pdf<br />\n<br />\n選民登記2020年<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">5月2日</span></strong>deadline<br />\n預4月分登記做選民<br />\n假設申請IT組織資格要1個月<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2月完結之前就要開始申請啦</strong></span>"},{"pid":"d5c4c86f269d2feb5469373d474a824b6e1979ff","tid":1897371,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:36:04.000Z","msg":"部份符合 IT 界選民資格的組織<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>A. IEEE 電機暨電子工程師學會</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ieee.org/membership/join/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ieee.org%2Fmembership%2Fjoin%2Findex.html&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=c63da161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ieee.org/membership/join/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>成為以下其中一種Professional Member組合：</ins><br />\n1) IEEE + IEEE Computer Society<br />\n2) IEEE + IEEE Communications Society<br />\n3) IEEE + IEEE Circuits and Systems Society<br />\n<br />\n<ins>入會資格</ins><br />\n- ICT Degree, 或<br />\n- 非 ICT Degree + 3 年 IT 工作經驗, 或<br />\n- 6 年 IT 工作經驗<br />\n<br />\n<ins>會員年費</ins><br />\n1) IEEE + IEEE Computer Society = US$158 + US$40 = US$198<br />\n2) IEEE + IEEE Communications Society = US$158 + US$33 = US$191<br />\n3) IEEE + IEEE Circuits and Systems Society = US$158 + US$22 = US$180<br />\n<br />\n記住申請<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Professional Member</strong></span>, 唔好揀左Student<br />\n申請過程會問你入咩society, 揀番自己想要既society就得<br />\n地址一定要填<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Hong Kong</span></strong>, 咁先會自動加入Hong Kong Section<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>B. 計算機學會(ACM-HK)</strong></ins> <a href=\"http://acmhk.cs.cityu.edu.hk/membership\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Facmhk.cs.cityu.edu.hk%2Fmembership&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=d5cb4c28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://acmhk.cs.cityu.edu.hk/membership</a><br />\n<br />\n需要首先申請成為 ACM Professional 會員<br />\n<a href=\"https://services.acm.org/public/qj/quickjoin/interim.cfm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fservices.acm.org%2Fpublic%2Fqj%2Fquickjoin%2Finterim.cfm&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=5339dae1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://services.acm.org/public/qj/quickjoin/interim.cfm</a><br />\n再登記成為香港分會 Professional 會員<br />\n<a href=\"http://acmhk.cs.cityu.edu.hk/regform.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Facmhk.cs.cityu.edu.hk%2Fregform.pdf&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=4d087e0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://acmhk.cs.cityu.edu.hk/regform.pdf</a><br />\n(將填好的表格電郵至Dr. Kenneth Lee: kenkclee@cityu.edu.hk )<br />\n<br />\n<ins>入會資格</ins><br />\nDegree + 兩年工作經驗<br />\n<br />\n<ins>會員年費</ins><br />\nUSA-ACM Professional Member = US$99<br />\nACM-HK Professional Member = HK$200 (網絡資料)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左以上兩樣之外仲有：<br />\n香港電腦學會(HKCS)、互聯網專業協會(iProA)、英國電腦學會（香港分會）(BCS-HK)、專業資訊保安協會(PISA)等<br />\n可以參考 <a href=\"https://www.charlesmok.hk/voter-registration/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.charlesmok.hk%2Fvoter-registration%2F&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=3c437e98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.charlesmok.hk/voter-registration/</a>"},{"pid":"b478af9f0ca461c72c04e61bb3a810091e721847","tid":1897371,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:45:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b095fac59bca23916bdf6f69b46382317a9eb05","tid":1897371,"uid":104035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:46:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff1133b7e45bb905b00c6923d84c7b76da83eedb","tid":1897371,"uid":295548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d5c4c86f269d2feb5469373d474a824b6e1979ff","tid":1897371,"uid":41355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:36:04.000Z","msg":"部份符合 IT 界選民資格的組織<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>A. IEEE 電機暨電子工程師學會</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ieee.org/membership/join/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ieee.org%2Fmembership%2Fjoin%2Findex.html&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=c63da161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ieee.org/membership/join/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>成為以下其中一種Professional Member組合：</ins><br />\n1) IEEE + IEEE Computer Society<br />\n2) IEEE + IEEE Communications Society<br />\n3) IEEE + IEEE Circuits and Systems Society<br />\n<br />\n<ins>入會資格</ins><br />\n- ICT Degree, 或<br />\n- 非 ICT Degree + 3 年 IT 工作經驗, 或<br />\n- 6 年 IT 工作經驗<br />\n<br />\n<ins>會員年費</ins><br />\n1) IEEE + IEEE Computer Society = US$158 + US$40 = US$198<br />\n2) IEEE + IEEE Communications Society = US$158 + US$33 = US$191<br />\n3) IEEE + IEEE Circuits and Systems Society = US$158 + US$22 = US$180<br />\n<br />\n記住申請<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Professional Member</strong></span>, 唔好揀左Student<br />\n申請過程會問你入咩society, 揀番自己想要既society就得<br />\n地址一定要填<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Hong Kong</span></strong>, 咁先會自動加入Hong Kong Section<br />\n<br />\n<br />\